The test only needs to be done by migrants with legal status
If you do not have this status , there is no audit and therefore no official work
Meanwhile , most of the host workers continue to be illegally in Russia .
&quot; Welcome &quot; or &quot; Enrived for unauthorized persons &quot;
Many migrants confirm that it is not easy to get official status in Russia .
The reason is bureaucratic hurdles and , of course , the linguistic difficulties
The legalization costs money : 12 to 16 thousand roubles .
A falsified registration can be done quickly and only for one and a half thousand
The staff of the Russian police know that our documents are mostly fake and we are not registered , and that is why there are cases of blackmail .
&quot; You want one or two hundred roubles for cigarettes and tea &quot; , the Taskschike Umed Huschkadamow speaks to journalists .
&apos;Do not waste costs for false papers &apos; .
