Some falsified certificates which certify the completion of the language test have already been seized by staff of the Federal Ministry of Migration .
The falsified papers were printed with a standard colour print .
Of course , the new owners did not get it : every miracle who hoped to save the tests would pay for the document sentausend Rubel .
This is more than twice as much the cost of the official test : this costs a migrant threw three thousand rubles .
