It is able to manipulate virtual objects in the air with just hands and to create virtual free space .
- Please be sure to get to know the research your group is conducting
- We are dealing with the interaction of man and machine , but we want to expand the limits of this interaction .
Until now , mankind has remained largely at the stage of being used with pixies on flat screens , sometimes even touching .
But we want 5-10 years to predict radical changes in this interaction .
For example , the Xboxx console and the child sensors are progress , and no Xbox is sold without kinetime because everyone is interested in motion control .
- What is the future in the future ?
- Although Kinenching has brought the interaction to a physical level , many still appear on the flat screen , sometimes in 3D .
The input of information ( the system receives more data ) has been improved , the output has not yet been decisive
We try to change this , work on genuine three-dimensional presentation systems based on various technologies , including projections .
We must make the computer world more complete in our physical world and make it more visible
This requires the user to recognize not only the user but also its surroundings .
Then we could be much more easily complemented by virtual objects .
And first of all , we should become this well-founded virtual reality helmets !
- What do you think about language control
It is popular but is it not over-estimated ?
- You are certainly not the sole solution because it raises questions about privacy because you do not always want to know all the rest about its actions and intentions .
In fact , every type of interaction with computers is good , but each of them is niche .
For example , we worked on the management of objects on public places on a project where we were experimenting with short and narrow tracks , instead of experimenting with excited gestures .
The gestures were not the object of the object but rather the shape of a brake that registered the movements of bones and muscles .
It is relatively large , but it could theoretically be reduced to the size of a flush wire .
