The first mention of this society was published in 1954 in November of the November issue of the magazine problematic , dedicated to four major articles of space .
The article by Prof. M. Subotowicz contains the proposal for the establishment of a space company
At the time , there were already the first satellite satellite projects , and it was clear that research would have a future .
