I still know how he said , when Mincy had a championship for Bayamon , he would provide a further one .
The Vaqueros championships were granted to him , but they were out of the way because he was already the top of the association in 1988 .
At that time he preferred to enjoy his full stakes and those of Mincy in the national team .
I still know when we won the World Cup in Mexico against the US for the first time .
Then came the World Championship in 1990 , where we were supposed to have the fourth place , which should have been Bronze , if not this Canadian arbitrator who had the last match for the second time , said Reyes .
Was this group of World Cup in 1990 the best national team you &apos;ve ever seen ?
She is one of the best , as well as those who won the Dream team in 2004 .
But my favourite is the team of the PanAmerican Games in Cuba in 1991 , where we won gold and offered a battle to the US team , as they did when they won a bronze in the World Cup .
